description:
A dusty old hat found in a pile of trash.
Surprisingly clean all things considered.
name: Hat

description: Some odd bits of fabric stitched together into a robe
name: Cloth

description: Puts your horrifying feet out of mind.
name: Shoes of Suppression

description:
The lid of a trash can. The smell is so bad it will
repel all danger! ...yeah, not really.
name: Trash Can Lid

description:
Cape made from only the lowest quality trash bag
(Mystery Effect)
name: Trash Bag Cape

description: More effective than stuffing your clothes with Manga
name: Padded Armor

description: Every adventure game begins with a shield
name: Wooden Shield

description: A handy defense for outdoor allergies
name: Pack of Tissues

description:
Book containing a step by step process for casting
wind magic: (teaches Storm Chaser)
name: Book of Storms

description:
Cracked old shield. Enchanted with an old spell to
make it magic resistant
name: Old Knight's Shield

description:
A horn from the Capricorn. Rediculously powerful
but so heavy it can encumber you.
name: Capricorn Horn

description: A handy and reliable Blue Jacket
name: Blue Jacket

description: A fairly normal looking cap
name: Cap

description: Never seems to use the dang thing
name: Toothbrush

description:
You never know when someone's just aching to sing
their heart out
name: Microphone

description: These allow you to push heavy blocks.
name: Stronghand Gloves

description:
An additciting phone game that sucks up your
attention: (teaches Cold Shoulder)
name: App Game

description:
Shield of a fallen warrior. The shield's owner will
take damage in place of hurt ally (+30 HP)
name: Noble Shield

description:
Strange piece of jewelry that harbors ill will
(10% chance of Physical Counter)
name: Revenge Brooch

description:
Scrap of paper once holding a Fairy. Seems to still
hold some faint power: (teaches Fairy Magic)
name: Fairy Dust Scrap

description: Hide Lunchbillion's true identity as a puny human!
name: Monster Disguise

description:
A shirt splashed with many colors. It's a great way
to stand out (Resist Light/Attack Target up)
name: Tye-Dye T-Shirt

description:
A black shirt with gothic designs
(Resist Darkness)
name: Gothic Shirt

description:
A soft bathrobe with "Hillsburgh Inn" embroidered on it
Not armor and provides little defense (Mystery effect)
name: Bathrobe

description:
A shirt, enchanted by powerful sunlight
(High Fire Resist/HP Regenerate)
name: Sunlight Shirt

description:
A shirt, enchanted by the power of the moon
(High Ice Resist/MP Regenerate)
name: Moonlight Shirt

description:
Gotta save the world in style
(Magic Defense)
name: Dress Shirt

description: A well worn windbreaker. Cozy and reliable
name: Black Jacket

description:
A cloak so charred in fire that it has become immune!
How does that work (Nullify Fire Damage)
name: Charred Cloak

description:
When you think of first aid, you probably think of
bandages: (teaches Patch Up)
name: First Aid Kit

description:
A flashlight with 3 settings; Bright, Bright and off:
(teaches Lightforce Storm)
name: Super Flashlight

description:
A book of puns, so awful they hurt. Make sure to wear
earplugs when reading these: (teaches Static Punchline)
name: Cursed Joke Book

description:
An unusual ring that fills the wearer with a new
confidence. (MAX HP Up/Low HP Regenerate)
name: Mcrae's Ring

description:
Utilize the powers of the Truth Clan
(Learn Skills as long as equipped)
name: Truth Ring

description:
A strange pair of pants that fills the wearer with 
unusual powers: (Learn Skills as long as equipped)
name: Soul Burning Buttocks

description:
Chipped stone of wind control. Still hold deadly wind
magic within: (teaches Ozone Cutter)
name: Cracked Wind Stone

description:
Please sign the waiver before consuming. You have
been warned: (teaches Sauce-pocalypse)
name: Ultra Hot Sauce

description:
A phone app for undead to talk on forums about anything
(teaches Explosive Hot Take)
name: Dead-It App

description:
A very very VERY long book about the process in which
Caterpillar becomes a butterfly. (teaches Sleep Breath)
name: Boring Book

description:
Small metal shield. Won't get in your way but it will
your enemy's!
name: Buckler
